[5] Cholera - China
Date: Tue 14 Oct 2014
Source: Xinhua News Agency [edited]
http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/china/2014-10/14/c_133716460.htm


Some 606 571 cases of infectious diseases were reported in September 2014, said the National Health and Family Planning Commission (NHFPC) in a statement. Among them, 3 cases of cholera were reported but none caused death. Cholera is categorized as Class A, the most serious category.

